Package: djt
Title: A toolbox to download Brazilian DJTs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
  person("Julio", "Trecenti", email = "jtrecenti@abj.org.br", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Caio", "Lente", email = "caio.lente@usp.br", role = c("aut")))
Description: This package makes it easy to download DJTs from TST's official
  website by providing the user with ways to filter dates, courts, booklets, etc.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
